1. *Sjajno* je ovo što se desilo! (This is wonderful that happened!)
2. Ona je *sjajno* odradio zadatak. (She did an excellent job on the task.)
3. Ona je pokazala *sjajnu* energiju. (She showed great energy.)
4. Ovo je *sjajno* mesto za odmor. (This is a great place for a vacation.)
5. *Sjajno* se slažemo! (We agree great!)
6. Ovo je *sjajno* rešenje za problem. (This is an excellent solution for the problem.)
7. Ova večera je bila *sjajna*. (This dinner was wonderful.)